Some games use the channel only for drums and the like, which take less than 4 KB. If this is the case for your game, you should be able to fit them into $C000-$CFFF, along with 12 KB of resident code.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Tue Nov 11, 2008 9:50 am</p><hr />
